result.execSummary:
The defendant Deandre S Manns was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Deandre S Manns is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Deandre S Manns was found guilty of Forgery-Uttering [Modifiers: as a Party to a Crime], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.38(2).
